{"tid":460722,"cid":17,"subCid":0,"title":"南美 旅遊攻略 【少圖】","createTime":"2017-11-07T01:52:30.000Z","updateTime":"2019-01-29T14:34:01.000Z","uid":157137,"like":27,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":31,"replies":[{"pid":"c19ef02ebdfa90f6266713d57f3f1e33ef2d75cd","tid":460722,"uid":157137,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-07T01:52:30.000Z","msg":"<div style=\"text-align: right;\">係呢度寫第一篇主要係想分享一下自己係南美自由行嘅經歷同埋小貼士，而家出住d以實用為主嘅文先，如果咁好彩有人睇我就會繼續po更加detailed同埋有相嘅遊記。小弟文筆差，麻煩大家唔好屌</div>我屌得太犀利<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n交通篇--長途巴士<br />\n<br />\n一般黎講backpackers係南美主要嘅交通工具都會係巴士。係呢度講一講我自己嘅經歷。咁多個國家入面質素（同埋價錢）最高嘅一定係阿根廷。多數時候係上車／落車果陣都會有條幫你擺／攞行李，記住要比貼士如果唔係可能佢會偷偷地碇走你個背囊<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n以下呢d網站可能對大家搵巴士飛/時間表有幫助：<br />\n<br />\n全南美 <a href=\"http://www.busbud.com\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.busbud.com&d=YLZVOCTtPfRM52Mv9ZxkNIzZXVCnaYNE8CBFJ%2F%2FgXXY%3D&h=b744609b\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">www.busbud.com</a><br />\n<br />\n智利 www.recorrido.cl<br />\n<br />\n玻利維亞 <a href=\"https://www.ticketsbolivia.com/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ticketsbolivia.com%2F&d=YLZVOCTtPfRM52Mv9ZxkNIzZXVCnaYNE8CBFJ%2F%2FgXXY%3D&h=70eed56f\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.ticketsbolivia.com/</a><br />\n<br />\n阿根廷<br />\n<a href=\"http://www.omnilineas.com\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.omnilineas.com&d=YLZVOCTtPfRM52Mv9ZxkNIzZXVCnaYNE8CBFJ%2F%2FgXXY%3D&h=04a82f1e\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">www.omnilineas.com</a><br />\n<a href=\"http://www.plataforma10.com.ar\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.plataforma10.com.ar&d=YLZVOCTtPfRM52Mv9ZxkNIzZXVCnaYNE8CBFJ%2F%2FgXXY%3D&h=93da6e2c\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">www.plataforma10.com.ar</a><br />\n<a href=\"http://www.busplus.com.ar\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.busplus.com.ar&d=YLZVOCTtPfRM52Mv9ZxkNIzZXVCnaYNE8CBFJ%2F%2FgXXY%3D&h=15a30598\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">www.busplus.com.ar</a><br />\n<br />\n巴西 <br />\n<a href=\"https://rodoviariaonline.com.br/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Frodoviariaonline.com.br%2F&d=YLZVOCTtPfRM52Mv9ZxkNIzZXVCnaYNE8CBFJ%2F%2FgXXY%3D&h=15c6f138\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://rodoviariaonline.com.br/</a><br />\n<a href=\"https://www.clickbus.com.br/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.clickbus.com.br%2F&d=YLZVOCTtPfRM52Mv9ZxkNIzZXVCnaYNE8CBFJ%2F%2FgXXY%3D&h=4373aea5\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.clickbus.com.br/</a><br />\n<br />\n秘魯<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.redbus.pe/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.redbus.pe%2F&d=YLZVOCTtPfRM52Mv9ZxkNIzZXVCnaYNE8CBFJ%2F%2FgXXY%3D&h=f7cc8d62\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.redbus.pe/</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n交通篇--飛機<br />\n<br />\n留意番如果大家要book內陸機嘅話，記住check下航空公司本地果個網站嘅價錢，因為好多時候會同國際／外國版有好大分別。<br />\n<br />\n舉個例，如果我上阿根廷航空(aerolineas argentinas)歐洲版網站book由buenos aires出發去bariloche嘅機票，來回最平都要港幣2600，不過係返阿根廷版book就只需1500！<br />\n<br />\n唯一就係秘魯嘅內陸機就唔可以用呢個方法book，因為佢寫明話係for residents only。如果大家係有儲開里數嘅話，不妨check下可唔可以換到飛，因為單係一程lima去cusco嘅機票都要成200美金。 不過其他南美國家（阿根廷，智利，巴西，哥倫比亞等）據我所知就無咁嘅限制。我自己亦都係智利同阿根廷用當地版網站book過內陸機，搭嘅時候完全無問題。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n交通篇--市內交通<br />\n係大城市入面嘅公共交通不外乎地鐵同巴士，係呢度就要同大家推介下一個app，叫moovit，以個人經驗黎講路線覆蓋率比起google maps多好多，不過estimated journey time就google準好多<br />\n<br />\n的士嘅話如果唔比人昆嘅話一般黎講唔會好貴。智利，阿根廷同巴西嘅的士價錢感覺上同香港差唔多，其他地方就好似多數無咪錶，要同司機講價，有d煩，如果唔識講西班牙文就更加大機會比人當水魚。<br />\n<br />\n當然有uber嘅地方我多數都會用，起碼安全d先。"},{"pid":"c985f92928938cc0b216c7f443cfed38f6bd0660","tid":460722,"uid":80736,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-07T01:52:44.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><div style=\"text-align: right;\">係呢度寫第一篇主要係想分享一下自己係南美自由行嘅經歷同埋小貼士，而家出住d以實用為主嘅文先，如果咁好彩有人睇我就會繼續po更加detailed同埋有相嘅遊記。小弟文筆差，麻煩大家唔好屌</div>我屌得太犀利<img src=\"/asset